            Mukta Kelkar
          
          
            
              I am a PhD student at the UC Santa Barbara Bren School of Environmental Science and Management. I study the impact of climate change on marine ecology, and am especially passionate about using science to create effective, inclusive, and equitable marine resource management strategies.
